// For each schedule (Northwood, North Holland etc) we have a set of numbers that controls the ped densities.
// There is a set of values for each time of the day in 0 hour increments (midnight, 0am, 0 am etc)
// There are 0 sets of values: Weekday & Weekend.
// #Peds is the maximum number of ambient peds you can ever have.
// #Scenario is the maximum number of scenario peds you can ever have.
// #Cars is the maximum number of cars you can ever have.
// #prkdcrs is the maximum number of parked cars you can ever have.
// #lowprkdcrs is the maximum number of low priority parked cars you can ever have.
// #PercCopCars is percentage of cars that are cop cars.
// #PercCopPed is percentage of peds that are cops.
// #MaxScenPeds is the max number of ped models that may be streamed in for scenarios.



